Prof George Wajackoyah has amassed a lot of fame in the short time he has thrown his hat into the presidential race
Little is known about the Adjunct Professor of Law before the 2022 candidature.
But, Prof Wajackoyah actually first announced his intention to vie to the Kenya’s top job in 2010.
In an interview on Citizen TV in 2011, Power Breakfast host Mutegi Njau said, “We used to refer to you as a fugitive and a mad man.”
Wajackoyah went ahead to disclose that he worked as a Police Constable, intelligence officer before moving to UK and US…